            <title><![CDATA[After leaving Respawn to work on Highguard, a former Apex Legends developer has been rehired by EA]]></title>
            <link>https://www.eurogamer.net/after-leaving-respawn-to-work-on-highguard-a-former-apex-legends-developer-has-been-rehired-by-ea</link>
            <guid>1474048</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
      <article data-ads="true" data-article-type="news" data-article-group="news" data-paywalled="false" data-premium="false" data-sponsored="false" data-type="article">


<header data-component="article-header">
  

    


  <p>

  <figure>
      <picture>
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/female-Apex-Legend-character-with-short-blond-hair-and-a-mostly-purple-outfit-giving-a-quick-thumbs-up-to-the-camera.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/female-Apex-Legend-character-with-short-blond-hair-and-a-mostly-purple-outfit-giving-a-quick-thumbs-up-to-the-camera.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.5&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1.5dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/female-Apex-Legend-character-with-short-blond-hair-and-a-mostly-purple-outfit-giving-a-quick-thumbs-up-to-the-camera.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.75&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1.75dppx)">
