        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/female-Apex-Legend-character-with-short-blond-hair-and-a-mostly-purple-outfit-giving-a-quick-thumbs-up-to-the-camera.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 1dppx)">
